OL,3,CDeath of four horses at racecourse
OL,4,C'not linked', investigation finds
OL,6,FThe death of four horses at a fixture
OL,7,Fat Newton Abbot were not linked and
OL,8,Feach had "unique circumstances"
OL,9,Fsurrounding them, an investigation has
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FFour horses died at the event held at
OL,13,FNewton Abbot racecourse on Tuesday 25
OL,14,FJune, believed to be the highest death
OL,15,Ftoll for a single afternoon of horse
OL,16,Fracing since 2007.
