OL,6,FThe British Horseracing Authority
OL,7,F(BHA) has since worked closely with
OL,8,Fcolleagues at Newton Abbot, to best
OL,9,Funderstand the circumstances behind
OL,10,Feach incident.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday 3 July it issued a
OL,13,Fstatement, following an inspection of
OL,14,Fthe racecourse and an assessment of
OL,15,Fits maintenance records.
