OL,3,CDeath of four horses at racecourse
OL,4,C'not linked', investigation finds
OL,6,FA statement released by the BHA said:
OL,7,F"The BHA's Racecourse and Facilities
OL,8,FManager is satisfied that there was no
OL,9,Fissue with the racing surface or any
OL,10,Fother facility at the track that
OL,11,Fcaused these incidents.
OL,13,F"This followed an inspection of
OL,14,Fconditions at Newton Abbot and a
OL,15,Fthorough assessment of the track's
OL,16,Fracing surface maintenance records.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
