OL,3,CDeath of four horses at racecourse
OL,4,C'not linked', investigation finds
OL,6,F"While the individual equine fatality
OL,7,Freviews are ongoing, it has been
OL,8,Fdetermined that each injury was
OL,9,Fsustained in unique circumstances and
OL,10,Fthere appears to be no external factor
OL,11,Flinking them.
OL,13,F"Newton Abbot's record demonstrates
OL,14,Fhow rare such occurrences are; in the
OL,15,Flast two full years, 2022 and 2023, a
OL,16,Ftotal of 1,524 runners competed at the
OL,17,Ftrack, resulting in three fatalities
OL,18,F(defined as a horse being fatally
OL,19,Finjured as a direct result of their
OL,20,Finjuries on the raceday or within 48
OL,21,Fhours of the raceday).
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
