OL,6,F"This equates to a fatal injury rate
OL,7,Fof 0.20%, below the current national
OL,8,FJumps average of 0.42%.
OL,10,F"In addition, a detailed investigation
OL,11,Fof the circumstances surrounding each
OL,12,Ffatality is being conducted by the
OL,13,FFatality Review Group.
OL,15,F"This process follows every fatality
OL,16,Fon all racedays."
